{"tid":751172,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【封殺港獨】1,200人上街勸港人醒覺 習總海報任踩","createTime":"2018-07-21T15:25:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-22T05:14:21.000Z","uid":73915,"like":50,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"7263d2cb43d5df88b54c45c2cb39de483043b4a5","tid":751172,"uid":73915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T15:25:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180721/58469382\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180721%2F58469382&d=laqLsuizk5Jpdifn%2FCRcuE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=296f0391\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180721%2F58469382&h=6629f4f5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180721/58469382</a><br />\n【新增動新聞】<br />\n香港自主權移交中國以來，政府未曾引用原意針對黑社會的《社團條例》取締過任何黑幫，卻首次動用該條例，取締提倡港獨、被指危害國家安全的香港民族黨，禁止其運作。民陣發起「23條近了，港人要醒覺」遊行，下午3時由灣仔修頓球場出發，遊行至警察總部外集會，抗議保安局破壞言論及結社自由。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180721/large/1532164834_f145.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180721%2Flarge%2F1532164834_f145.jpg&h=a3d64334&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180721/large/1532165018_dbcd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180721%2Flarge%2F1532165018_dbcd.jpg&h=3c133819&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180721/large/1532165391_04e3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180721%2Flarge%2F1532165391_04e3.jpg&h=c9369d42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180721/large/1532165333_e40a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.l